file.name: test_openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  version: 0.1
  description: Currency service
  title: Currencies
paths:
  '/currencies':
    get:
      summary: Get All Currencies
      operationId: currencies.index
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/page'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/perPage'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/Currency'
  '/currencies/{uuid}':
    get:
      summary: Get a Currency
      operationId: currencies.show
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/uuid'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Currency'
        '404':
          description: Currency not found for `uuid`.
components:
  parameters:
    page:
      name: page
      in: query
      description: Returns the page contents for the specified page number from the paginated result of the search.
      schema:
        type: integer
        minimum: 1
        default: 1
    perPage:
      name: per_page
      in: query
      description: Specifies how many items to return in each page of results.
      schema:
        type: integer
        minimum: 1
        default: 10
    uuid:
      name: uuid
      in: path
      required: true
      description: Resource UUID.
      schema:
        type: string
        maxLength: 255
        format: uuid
        default: desc
  schemas:
    Currency:
      x-mdsol:
        resource: currencies
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          description: Name of the currency.
          type: string
        code:
          description: '[ISO 4217](https://www.iso.org/iso-4217-currency-codes.html) three-letter code for the currency.'
          type: string
        symbol:
          description: Symbol of the currency.
          type: string
        uuid:
          description: Database-independent universally unique identifier.
          type: string
          format: uuid
      example:
        {
          "uuid": "67c397fc-caff-11e7-abc4-cec278b6b50a",
          "code": "AED",
          "symbol": "د.إ",
          "name": "United Arab Emirates Dirham"
        }
